Portions of this product incorporate code from:
- Mangayomi (Apache 2.0) — extension system, manga reader, anime player, download manager, HTTP stack
- Aniyomi (Apache 2.0) — anime player concepts, AniSkip, episode model, hoster abstraction
- Flutter (BSD-3-Clause) — UI framework
- Riverpod (MIT) — state management
- Isar (Apache 2.0) — local database
- GoRouter (BSD-3-Clause) — routing
- flex_color_scheme (BSD-3-Clause) — theming
- media_kit (MIT) — video player (libmpv)
- extended_image (MIT) — image loading and gestures
- photo_view (MIT) — pinch-zoom
- flutter_html (MIT) — HTML rendering for novels

Native libraries:
- libmpv (LGPL-2.1+) — video playback engine
- FFmpeg (LGPL/GPL) — media processing (dynamic linking)

